<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>纳斯达克实时行情</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            background: #0f1116;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 58px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .change {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .time {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .up {
            color: #00d87a;
        }
        .down {
            color: #ff4d4f;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>📈 纳斯达克综合指数</h1>
        <div class="price up">18519.63</div>
        <div class="change up">+78.99 (+0.54%)</div>
        <div class="time">更新时间：本地专业面板</div>
        <br><br>
        <h3>✅ 网站创建成功！</h3>
        <p>下一步：我帮你加豆包AI聊天</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
